section.section:
The document entitled "STATEMENT ABOUT TENANCY" shall:
Be on a separate sheet of paper attached to the contract for the sale or transfer of a residence in default;
Be dated and personally signed by the homeowner and the purchaser and be witnessed and acknowledged by a notary public appointed and commissioned by the State;
Contain a statement informing the homeowner of the homeowner's right to a copy of a signed lease; and
Contain the following statement printed in at least 15 point type:
